  <Description>A docker running gluster server. This allows me to use a folder in the Unraid cache pool as persistent storage for Kubernetes / Docker Swarm through glusterfs. It works way better than NFS, especially for high-availability applications.&#13;
&#13;
For more detail readme, please refer to https://github.com/testdasi/gluster-server</Description>
